%3BWhen%20you%20get%20into%20the%20space%20of%20AI%20experimentation%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20things%20to%20do%20is%20not%20kill%20innovation%20when%20you're%20starting%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20is%20touching%20on%20the%20reality%20of%20AI%20adoption%20at%20many%20companies.%20Even%20as%20firms%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-google-engineers-coding-productive-sundar-pichai-alphabet-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eproductivity%20gains%20from%20AI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20employees'%20days%20haven't%20necessarily%20gotten%20any%20shorter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-manager-ai-reduces-busywork-not-daily-workload-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOne%20Microsoft%20manager%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20AI%20tools%20cut%20his%20coding%20time%20%E2%80%94%20which%20used%20to%20make%20up%20the%20overwhelming%20majority%20of%20his%20workload%20%E2%80%94by%2070%25%2C%20yet%20his%20overall%20workload%20didn't%20shrink.%20Many%20leaders%20have%20also%20said%20that%20AI%20will%20free%20up%20employees'%20time%2C%20so%20they%20can%20focus%20on%20more%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20rather%20than%20suggesting%20that%20workers%20might%20get%20more%20free%20time%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20said%20that%20when%20leaders%20push%20AI%20adoption%2C%20they%20need%20to%20make%20it%20%26quot%3Breally%20relevant%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20day-to-day%20work%20of%20employees%2C%20rather%20than%20making%20it%20another%20ask%20from%20their%20manager.%20It%20should%20be%20framed%20as%20a%20tool%20that%20helps%20employees%20reclaim%20a%20percentage%20of%20their%20day%2C%20the%20CPO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20employees%20would%20be%20glad%20to%20save%20time%20spent%20on%20work%2C%20and%20she%20said%20companies%20get%20it%20wrong%20by%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3Bhere's%20three%20new%20things%20that%20we%