regon%20State%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20it's%20a%20standard%20setup%20that%20allows%20the%20robot%20to%20learn%20by%20mimicking%20its%20operator.%20Aitken%20said%20OpenAI's%20GELLO%20strategy%20could%20present%20an%20advantage%20over%20AI%20companies%20that%20use%20motion%20capture%20suits.%20It's%20cheaper%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20because%20each%20controller%20maps%20directly%20to%20a%20robot%20arm%2C%20the%20robot%20can%20more%20easily%20learn%20how%20specific%20human%20movements%20translate%20into%20its%20own%20motions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20San%20Francisco%2C%20OpenAI%20runs%20three%20shifts%20and%20a%20few%20dozen%20workstations%20that%20collect%20data%20around%20the%20clock%2C%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20lab%20said.%20Cameras%20record%20both%20the%20operator%20and%20the%20robot%20performing%20tasks%2C%20and%20workers%20are%20rated%20on%20how%20many%20%26quot%3Bgood%20hours%26quot%3B%20of%20functional%20training%20data%20they%20can%20generate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217110904-bc9e-4481-96c9-3209ae3dbfb8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Very%20early%20in%20the%20process'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reliance%20on%20contract%20workers%20and%20performance%20metrics%20mirrors%20how%20AI%20companies%2C%20including%20OpenAI%2C%20have%20historically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-training-jobs-data-annotators-labelers-outlier-scale-meta-xai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Escaled%20data%20labeling%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20their%20large%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20companies%20are%20hoping%20if%20you%20collect%20enough%20of%20this%20data%2C%20you%20can%20translate%20it%20into%20robot%20motions%2C%20and%20they%20will%20get%20a%20scaling%20effect%20and%20have%20this%20ChatGPT%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Fern%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20something%20that%20hasn't%20been%20proven%20out%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20s