0projects%20are%20fully%20financed%2C%20the%20syndication%20effort%20by%20JPMorgan%20had%20been%20successful%20overall%2C%20and%20that%20the%20slowdown%20in%20new%20participants%20hadn't%20alarmed%20bankers%20given%20that%20it%20was%20at%20the%20tail%20end%20of%20such%20a%20large%20debt%20offering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20person%20acknowledged%20that%20banks%20and%20institutional%20investors%20had%20also%20grown%20wary%20in%20recent%20months%20of%20taking%20on%20too%20much%20exposure%20to%20Oracle%2C%20a%20tech%20giant%20whose%20credit%20rating%20sits%20below%20some%20of%20its%20peers%20in%20the%20AI%20race%2C%20including%20Microsoft%20and%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reticence%20among%20lenders%20and%20investors%20to%20continue%20bankrolling%20Stargate%20raises%20questions%20about%20whether%20the%20mega-project%20will%20meet%20its%20lofty%20objectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20hearing%20from%20market%20participants%20that%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20there%20may%20be%20banks%20that%20could%20be%20approaching%20the%20exposure%20levels%20they're%20comfortable%20with%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20certain%20data%20center%20projects%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dhaval%20Shah%2C%20a%20director%20at%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Infrastructure%20Ratings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20unprecedented%20data%20center%20development%20cycle%20has%20been%20dominated%20by%20just%20a%20handful%20of%20leading%20players%2C%20testing%20whether%20lenders%20and%20investors%20will%20remain%20willing%20to%20continue%20to%20accrue%20heavy%20exposure%20to%20borrowers%20like%20Oracle.%20Oracle%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20credit%20default%20swaps%20that%20insure%20against%20losses%20on%20Oracle's%20corporate%20debt%20rose%20in%20cost%2C%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20concerns%20around%20the%20company's%20enormous%20spending%20on%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%2C%20the%20AI%20chatbot%20maker%20that%20will%20anchor%20the%20Stargate%20facilities%2C%20meanwhile%2