%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20pipeline%20%26quot%3Bputs%20us%20on%20a%20clear%20path%20to%20securing%20the%20full%20%24500%20billion%2C10-gigawatt%20commitment%26quot%3B%20it%20had%20announced%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20financing%20for%20the%20project%2C%20so%20far%2C%20has%20been%20provided%20by%20major%20financial%20institutions%20that%20have%20banded%20together%20to%20share%20its%20immense%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20its%20risks%20%E2%80%94%20in%20what%20are%20known%20as%20syndication%20deals.%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20and%20Mitsubishi%20UFJ%20Financial%20Group%20led%20the%20syndication%20effort%20for%20the%20two%20Stargate%20projects%20in%20Shackelford%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20Port%20Washington%2C%20Wisconsin.%20Both%20banks%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20is%20leading%20a%20syndication%20to%20finance%20another%20Stargate%20data%20center%20campus%20in%20Michigan.%20A%20person%20familiar%20with%20that%20effort%20said%20that%20it%20has%20attracted%20interest%20from%20syndication%20takers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20group%20of%20lenders%20provided%20about%20%2418%20billion%20of%20financing%20for%20another%20Stargate%20facility%20in%20New%20Mexico%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-11-07%2Fbanks-lend-18-billion-for-oracle-tied-data-center-in-new-mexico%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitial%20players%20in%20large%20syndication%20deals%20often%20seek%20to%20sell%20off%20portions%20of%20their%20loan%20commitments%20to%20other%20players%2C%20including%20other%20banks%20and%20institutional%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20sale%20of%20these%20positions%2C%20which%20is%20done%20to%20reap%20quick%20profits%20and%20lower%20exposure%2C%20has%20become%20trickier%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Stargate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20bankers%20and%20a%20financing%20executive%20who%20are%20familiar%20with%20the%20syndication%20market%20said%20that%20the%20rising%20perception%20of%20risk%20around%20Stargate%20meant%20that%20lenders%20now%20wanted%20higher%20yields%20to%20lend%20to%20it.%20That%20has%20placed%20recent%20Stargate%20syndicators%20in%20a%20position%20where%20they%20can%20no%20longer%20profitably%20sell%20off%20debt%20that%20was%20arranged%20at%20tighter%20spreads%20just%20a%20few%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStargate%20borrowing%20rates%20may%20not%20come%20down%20any%20time%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Ratings%20affirmed%20Oracle's%20rating%20at%20BBB%20but%20said%20it%20was%20considering%20a%20cut%20due%20to%20the%20company's%20enormous%20planned%20spending%20on%20AI%20infrastructure.%20A%20downgrade%20below%20BBB%20minus%20would%20place%20a%20junk%20rating%20on%20Oracle%20debt%2C%20raising%20its%20borrowing%20costs%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20surprised%20these%20loans%20were%20even%20underwritten%20at%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Luria%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20market%20has%20indicated%20this%20is%20not%20investment-grade%20debt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Luria%20said%20one%20scenario%20in%20particular%20could%20make%20the%20loans%20less%20risky.%20OpenAI%20is%20now%20in%20the%20process%20of%20trying%20to%20raise%20as%20much%20as%20%24100%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20reports%2C%20giving%20the%20Stargate%20venture%20a%20potential%20cushion%20of%20equity%20and%20making%20its%20debt%20easier%20to%20sell%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20that%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Beverybody's%20dreams%20come%20true.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20bankers%20who%20spoke%20with%20Business%20Insider%20said%20the%20slowdown%20did%20not%20indicate%20acute%20trouble%20in%20the%20syndication%20market%2C%20but%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20pool%20of%20investors%20who%20still%20have%20an%20appetite%20for%20the%20Stargate%20debt%20has%20shrunk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20we%20have%20enough%20digestive%20capacity%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20market%20for%20investors%20to%20buy%20all%20of%20the%20debt%20that%20will%20be%20required%2C%20said%20David%20Tawil%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20transaction%20insurance%20advisory%20firm%20Castle%20Harbour.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20market's%20real%20concern%3A%20the%20size%20of%20this%20whole%20movement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-openai-stargate-loans-jpmorgan-diminishing-interest-debt-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1769076901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69711009d3c7faef0eccaa1a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-openai-stargate-loans-jpmorgan-diminishing-interest-debt-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Appetite%20for%20loans%20tied%20to%20Oracle's%20data%20center%20partnership%20with%20OpenAI%20has%20diminished%2C%20reflecting%20concerns%20over%20credit%20risk%20and%20AI%20investment%20scale.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dcampbell%2Bweb%40insider.com%20(Dakin%20Campbell%2CDaniel%20Geiger)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-openai-stargate-loans-jpmorgan-diminishing-interest-debt-2026-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Millions%20In%20US%20Brace%20For%20Potentially%20Catastrophic%20Ice%20Storm%3A%20What%20To%20Know%20By%20Numbers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Millions%20of%20Americans%20from%20New%20Mexico%20to%20the%20Carolinas%20are%20bracing%20for%20a%20potentially%20catastrophic%20ice%20storm%20that%20could%20crush%20trees%20and%20power%20lines%20and%20knock%20out%20power%20for%20days.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1769076807000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-12%2Fk0dtvo7_us-storm-afp_625x300_01_December_19.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorith