ures%2C%20and%20I'm%20fighting%20to%20keep%20my%20business%20viable.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225484%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fisayo%20Che%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6970eccdd3c7faef0ecca455%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224113%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFisayo%20Che%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20fashion%20brand%20Elisamama%2C%20counted%20on%20Saks%20for%20more%20than%20half%20of%20her%20business.%20The%20company's%20bankruptcy%20has%20left%20her%20questioning%20a%20yearslong%20partnership.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Fisayo%20Che%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFisayo%20Che%20founded%20Elisamama%2C%20a%20clothing%20brand%20that%20is%20sold%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaks-bankruptcy-looms-how-crisis-unfolded-2026-1%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESaks%20Fifth%20Avenue%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20retailer's%20parent%20company%2C%20Saks%20Global%2C%20filed%20for%20Chapter%2011%20bankruptcy%20and%20owes%20her%20six%20figures.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%2C%20Che%20is%20struggling%20to%20trust%20her%20longtime%20partner%20and%20make%20up%20for%20the%20lost%20revenue.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Fisayo%20Che%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20women's%20wear%20brand%20Elisamama.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20Che's%20statements%2C%20including%20the%20amount%20Saks%20owes%2C%20with%20documentation%20she%20provided.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESaks%20Global%20filed%20in%20January%20for%20Chapter%2011%20bankruptcy%20protection%2C%20which%20allows%20it%20to%20continue%20operating%20while%20undergoing%20a%20court-supervised%20reorganization%20of%20its%20debt.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20Saks%20said%20it%20is%20committed%20to%20%26quot%3Btrusted%20relationships%20with%20brand%20partners%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20funding%20it%20secured%20through%20the%20bankruptcy%20will%20%26quot%3Bfacilitate%20go-forward%20payments%20to%20brand%20partners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecoming%20a%20fashion%20designer%20was%20never%20a%20part%20of%20my%20vision%20board.%20When%20I%20founded%20Elisamama%2C%20I%20was%20still%20working%20a%20corporate%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20like%20I%20wanted%20to%20live%20a%20life%20of%20more%20meaning%20and%20purpose.%20My%20family%20is%20from%20Nigeria%2C%20and%20I%20spent%20time%20there%20growing%20up.%20I%20got%20the%20idea%20to%20start%20a%20brand%20that%20supports%20women%20artisans%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElisamama%20is%20a%20women's%20wear%20and%20children's%20brand%20inspired%20by%20African%20artistry%20and%20prints.%20At%20first%2C%20I%20sold%20the%20clothing%20at%20flea%20markets%3B%20later%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscaled-etsy-shop-48k-profit-in-four-months-using-data-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elisted%20on%20Etsy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20promoted%20it%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaks%20really%20gave%20my%20business%20a%20platform%20to%20grow.%20Now%2C%20it's%20going%20through%20bankruptcy%20and%20hasn't%20paid%20me%20for%20some%20of%20my%20inventory.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20how%20to%20trust%20the%20company%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2236760cf3-8fcc-4f4e-af99-a9c8d7b91ad3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20flea%20markets%20to%20Fifth%20Avenue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fall%20of%202020%2C%20someone%20found%20us%20on%20Instagram%20and%2C%20unbeknownst%20to%20me%2C%20dropped%20our%20name%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaks-bankruptcy-money-woed-brands-vendors-chanel-burberry-gucci-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESaks%20buyer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20department%20store%20initially%20reached%20out%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20scam%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20respond.%20Then%2C%20a%20vice%20president%C2%A0from%20the%20company%C2%A0DM'd%20me%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20freaked%20out%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewas%20very%20scared.%20I%20thought%3A%20How%20are%20we%20going%20to%20do%20this%3F%20I%20even%20told%20them%20I%20needed%20time%20to%20figure%20it%20out%20because%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20mess%20up%20this%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaks%20really%20walked%20alongside%20us%2C%20gave%20us%20guidance%2C%20and%20helped%20us%20dip%20our%20toes%20slowly%20into%20its%20world.%20It%20was%20rapid-fire%20learning%2C%20trying%20to%20understand%20all%20the%20vendor%20requirements%2C%20including%20shipping%20and%20routing%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20hired%20more%20artisans%20in%20Nigeria.%20We%20beefed%20up%20our%20production.%20We%20worked%20on%20our%20supply%20situation.%20Everybody%20was%20winning%3B%20it%20helped%20us%20help%20other%20people%20grow%20their%20own%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Saks%20selected%20us%20to%20join%20its%20New%20Wave%20program%20for%20emerging%20designers.%20We%20came%20to%20New%20York%2C%20connected%20with%20industry%20experts%20and%20the%20press%2C%20and%20the%20company%20gave%20us%20a%20grant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%2C%20we%20had%20our%20products%20placed%20in%20the%20window%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaks-fifth-avenue-department-store-visit-bankruptcy-images-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESaks'%20flagship%20store%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20New%20York.%20That%20was%20a%20remarkable%20moment%20for%20me%20and%20my%20team%20in%20Nigeria%2C%20who%20are%20so%20proud%20of%20this%20work.%20It%20was%20nothing%20that%20I%20could%20even%20have%20imagined%20for%20Elisamama.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exposure%20it%20gave%20us%20was%20significant%20and%20gave%20us%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20signed%20with%20a%20showroom%20and%C2%A0started%20selling%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshopmy-top-best-selling-brands-influencer-affiliate-marketing-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretailers%20like%20Shopbop%2C%20Tuckernuck%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20several%20specialty%20boutiques.%20Things%20were%20ramping%20up%2C%20and%20the%20more%20I%20did%20this%20work%2C%20the%20more%20joy%20I%20found%20in%20it.%20In%202024%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-six-figure-job-build-fashion-business-still-questions-decision-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleft%20my%20corporate%20job%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22elisamama%20in%20saks'%20weekend%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6970ee63a645d1188187b545%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElisamama%20was%20featured%20in%20Saks%20Fifth%20Avenue's%20window%20display%20in%202023.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Fisayo%20Che%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b1cd7f8-355d-4a38-817d-9e6a51d9cc25%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20a%20great%20partner%20broke%20my%20trust%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESaks%20has%20been%20a%20great%20partner%20to%20us.%20It%20has%20placed%20orders%20with%20us%20every%20season%20since%202020.%20It's%2050%25%20or%2060%25%20of%20our%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problems%20started%20in%20February%20of%20last%20year%2C%20when%20Saks%20sent%20vendors%20a%20memo%20about%20paying%20in%20installments.%20Prior%20to%20that%2C%20we%20were%20consistently%20paid%20on%20the%20agreed-upon%20payment%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%3A%20We%20can%20wait%20a%20few%20months%20to%20get%20paid.%20They're%20important%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20a%20check%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20hundred%20dollars%20in%20July%2C%20and%20in%20August%2C%20we%20were%20paid%20a%20more%20substantial%20amount.%20I%20thought%20we%20were%20back%20on%20track%20and%20kept%