rysler%20Pacifica.%20We've%20had%20five%20cars%20totaled%20in%20the%20past%20year%2C%20but%20because%20I%20hold%20a%20dealer's%20license%20and%20buy%20vehicles%20wholesale%20at%20auctions%2C%20we've%20been%20able%20to%20replace%20them%20and%20even%20come%20out%20ahead%20on%20insurance%20payouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f76549bc-3284-432e-b284-caa909949920%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20price%20difference%20compared%20to%20traditional%20rental%20companies%20is%20huge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMike%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEnterprise%20once%20quoted%20me%20%24805%20for%20an%20SUV%20from%20Friday%20to%20Sunday.%20Turo%20cost%20us%20%24360%20for%20four%20days%20and%20600%20miles%20when%20we%20rented%20that%20Escalade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDarlene%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20listed%20mom's%20Corolla%20as%20a%20trial%2C%20but%20the%20first%20renter%20kept%20extending%20her%20trip%20week%20after%20week%2C%20and%20it%20ended%20up%20being%202.5%20months%20total.%20The%20car%20was%20gone%2C%20and%20we%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%2C%20so%20we%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet's%20add%20another.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20start%2C%20we%20reinvested%20every%20dollar%20back%20into%20the%20business.%20That's%20how%20we%20grew%20to%2010%20cars%20in%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20choose%20Turo's%2060%25%20protection%20plan%3A%20we%20keep%2060%25%2C%20Turo%20takes%2040%25%2C%20but%20our%20deductible%20is%20lower.%20Hosts%20can%20take%20up%20to%2090%25%20but%20risk%20a%20much%20higher%20deductible.%20Understanding%20that%20trade-off%20is%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMike%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Day-to-day%2C%20I'm%20checking%20cars%20in%20and%20out%2C%20cleaning%2C%20handling%20inspections%2C%20and%20keeping%20up%20with%20competition%20in%20the%20Atlanta%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20my%20IT%20job%20last%20April%20after%20paying%20off%20all%20my%20debts.%20I%20was%20breathing%20and%20dreaming%20of%20Turo%20at%20work.%20Now%20it's%20my%20focu