8bf-68cd-4277-9e9c-abc0111f1726%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnother%20challenge%20is%20time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDarlene%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Most%20people%20start%20Turo%20while%20working%20full-time.%20You%20need%20excellent%20planning%20and%20time%20management.%20We%20learned%20the%20hard%20way%3A%20clean%20a%20car%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20on%2C%20we'd%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI'll%20do%20it%20in%20the%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20then%20get%20a%207%20a.m.%20booking.%20At%205%20a.m.%2C%20with%20car%20washes%20closed%2C%20you're%20in%20the%20driveway%20scrubbing%2C%20photographing%2C%20and%20prepping%20the%20car.%20Now%20it's%20a%20habit%3A%20the%20car%20comes%20in%2C%20and%20it%20gets%20cleaned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMike%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Revenue%20now%20depends%20on%20the%20season%20and%20the%20vehicle.%20Our%20Corolla%20rents%20for%20%2442%20to%20%2446%20per%20day.%20Some%20cars%20earn%20%24800%20a%20month%2C%20while%20others%20earn%20%241%2C200%20during%20peak%20season%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20which%20typically%20spans%20from%20March%20to%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20still%20making%20six%20figures%20in%20profit%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22557203e3-eaa1-4da5-b705-037cb5b576a9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20biggest%20advice%3A%20do%20your%20homework%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDarlene%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECheck%20Turo's%20website%20for%20rules%2C%20like%20no%20cars%20older%20than%2012%20years%20or%20with%20more%20than%20130%2C000%20miles%20when%20listed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWatch%20videos%20from%20Turo%20hosts%20on%20YouTube%2C%20but%20vet%20their%20advice.%20Don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20ask%20experienced%20hosts%20for%20guidance.%20Mike%20and%20I%20mentor%20people%20all%20the%20time%3B%20we%20love%20helping%20new%20hosts%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20long-term%20goal%20is%20to%20become%20Atlanta's%20go-to%20personal%20car%20rental%20company.%20We're%20proud%20of%20what%20we've%20built%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20prouder%20to%20do%20it%20together%20as%20siblings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-sibling-duo-built-6-figure-car-rental-business-turo-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1769076301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696fd8cbd3c7faef0ecc95f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-sibling-duo-built-6-figure-car-rental-business-turo-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Michael%20Rumph%20and%20Darlene%20Person%2C%20siblings%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20built%20a%20profitable%2013-car%20Turo%20fleet%20that%20started%20with%20their%20mother's%20car%20in%202022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kaila%20Yu)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-sibling-duo-built-6-figure-car-rental-business-turo-2026-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Too%20Dangerous%20To%20Go%20To%20Hospital'%3A%20Glimpse%20Into%20Iran's%20Protest%20Crackdown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Young%20protesters%20shot%20in%20the%20back%2C%20shotgun%20pellets%20fired%20in%20a%20doctor's%20face%2C%20wounded%20people%20afraid%20to%20go%20to%20hospital%3A%20%26quot%3BEvery%20family%20has%20been%20affected%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20deadly%20crackdown%20on%20Iran's%20recent%20wave%20of%20demonstrations.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1769076146000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-01%2Fsgg2pgq4_iran-protests_625x300_13_January_26.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftoo-dangerous-to-go-to-hospital-a-glimpse-into-irans-protest-crackdown-10824641%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Young%20protesters%20shot%20in%20the%20back%2C%20shotgun%20pellets%20fired%20in%20a%20doctor