3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egovernment's%20latest%20dietary%20guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggest%20people%20drink%20whole%20milk%20instead%20of%20low-fat.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20matters%20a%20lot%20for%20school%20lunches%2C%20where%20whole%20milk%20will%20get%20top%20billing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20us%3A%20Who%20actually%20prefers%20sludgy%2C%20thick%20whole%20milk%20over%20crisp%20skim%3F%20Yuck!%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20refuse%20the%20long%20arm%20of%20the%20government's%20reach%20into%20my%20refrigerator%3A%20I'm%20not%20drinking%20whole%20milk!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20readily%20accept%20that%20food%20is%20political%2C%20so%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frfk-new-dietary-guidelines-5-changes-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elatest%20dietary%20guidelines%20from%20the%20US%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20say%20to%20drink%20whole%20milk%20instead%20of%20skim%20%E2%80%94%20are%20being%20seen%20as%20the%20latest%20political%20battle%20isn't%20a%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20something%20in%20the%20latest%20whole%20milk%20debate%20that%20is%20truly%20confusing%20to%20me.%20It's%20that%20%E2%80%A6%20whole%20milk%20isn't%20very%20good%3F%20And%20I%20don't%20think%20many%20of%20us%20have%20felt%20we%20couldn't%20drink%20it%20because%20of%20government%20guidelines.%20We%20just%20don't%20like%20it!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223a0bc249-b776-4147-9ef2-468442d053eb%5C%22%3EWhole%20milk%20as%20a%20win%20for%20freedom%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESecretary%20of%20Health%20and%20full-fat%20dairy%20booster%20Robert%20Kennedy%20Jr.%20is%20a%20polarizing%20figure%2C%20so%20people%20are%20going%20to%20interpret%20this%20kind%20of%20video%20in%20a%20way%20that%20fits%20their%20worldview%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22qme%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%F0%9F%A5%9B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FQUeSfR7EC8%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FQUeSfR7EC8%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Secretary%20Kennedy%20(%40SecKennedy)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSecKennedy%2Fstatus%2F2011894691705585764%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2015%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20positioning%20this%20change%20as%20people%20being%20desperate%20to%20drink%20whole%20milk%20but%20feeling%20they%20weren't%20allowed%20to.%20That%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20settle%20for%20skim%20or%202%25%20milk%2C%20and%20finally%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20are%20allowed%20the%20verboten%20pleasures%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223eba953e-c50a-42cb-8fa2-1e1eb5351008%5C%22%3EHere's%20MY%20beef%3A%20Whole%20milk%20is%20gross.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhole%20milk%20is%20too%20sludgy%2C%20too%20thick.%20It%20always%20kind%20of%20smells%20like%20it's%20on%20its%20way%20to%20turning%20sour.%20I%20find%20the%20white%20residue%20it%20leaves%20on%20the%20sides%20of%20a%20glass%20off-putting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYuck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne-percent%20milk%20is%20crisp%2C%20drinkable%2C%20watery%2C%20cold%2C%20and%20refreshing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreat%20to%20drink%20on%20its%20own%20or%20as%20a%20bath%20for%20cereal.%20Personally%2C%20I%20think%20skim%20is%20too%20watery%2C%20and%202%25%20too%20close%20to%20whole%2C%20but%20I%20accept%20those%20options%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20it's%20not%20any%20fear%20of%20fat%20intake%20that%20has%20kept%20me%20from%20buying%20whole%20milk%3B%20it's%20that%20whole%20milk%20is%20stinky%20and%20gross.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20should%20note%20here%20that%20the%20health%20benefits%20of%20whole%20vs.%20low-fat%20milk%20are%20a%20living%2C%20breathing%20debate.%20Whole%20milk%20has%20more%20