%20the%20new%20%26quot%3BDietary%20Guidelines%20for%20Americans%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20include%20favoring%20whole%20milk.%20Yuck.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2215b37223-9813-41ab-93de-2eeb377215d1%5C%22%3EYes%2C%20I'm%20sure%20there%20are%20some%20of%20you%20out%20there%20who%20are%20adult%20whole%20milk%20fans%20and%20prefer%20it%20over%20skim.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20whole%20milk%3F%20Know%20that%20I%20see%20you%2C%20I%20accept%20you%2C%20and%20you%20are%20valid.%20It's%20fine%20to%20have%20a%20taste%20preference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20simply%20don't%20believe%20there%20are%20throngs%20of%20adults%20out%20there%20who've%20been%20feeling%20forced%20to%20choke%20down%202%25%20when%20they%20were%20dying%20for%20whole%20milk.%20You're%20a%20grownup!%20Buy%20whatever%20milk%20you%20like!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20main%20point%20of%20the%20latest%20guidelines%20isn't%20really%20aimed%20at%20making%20suggestions%20to%20adults.%20The%20actionable%20part%20of%20the%20guidelines%20is%20that%20they%20inform%20the%20rules%20for%20federal%20food%20programs%20for%20kids%2C%20like%20the%20National%20School%20Lunch%20Program%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubscriber.politicopro.com%2Farticle%2F2026%2F01%2Ftrump-signs-bill-allowing-schools-to-offer-whole-milk-00728907%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20only%20allowed%20low-fat%20milk%20options%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20really%20care%20if%20a%20kid%20prefers%20whole%20or%20skim%20milk%20with%20their%20sloppy%20Joe%20or%20PB%26amp%3BJ%20%E2%80%94%20either%20option%20seems%20better%20to%20me%20than%20chocolate%20milk%2C%20which%2C%20according%20to%20my%20own%20elementary%20school%20children%2C%20is%20what%20everyone%20chooses%20at%20lunch%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20government%20is%20going%20to%20start%20meddling%20more%20with%20school%20lunches%2C%20frankly%2C%20I'd%20welcome%20them