%20has%20improved%20his%20mental%20health%20and%20rekindled%20his%20love%20of%20technology.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Derek%20Fulton%2C%2031%2C%20a%20former%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-internal-emails-software-sales-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENvidia%20software%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20engineer%20who%20quit%20to%20found%20the%20North%20Carolina-based%20cloud%20startup%20Carolina%20Cloud%20with%20his%20wife.%20Nvidia%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20about%20its%20work%20culture.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20messing%20around%20with%20computers%20since%20I%20got%20my%20first%20MacBook%20in%202006%20at%20age%2011.%20From%20building%20potato%20cannons%20to%20flying%20drones%2C%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20solve%20problems%20and%20build%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20college%2C%20I%20worked%20in%20data%20science%20at%20a%20European%20bank%20and%20as%20a%20quantitative%20analyst%20at%20a%20hedge%20fund%20specializing%20in%20mortgage%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20friend%20from%20college%20who%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-leaders-gained-lost-staff-tech-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworked%20at%20Nvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20posted%20on%20LinkedIn%20about%20a%20software%20engineering%20opportunity%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20apply.%20I've%20always%20been%20a%20technologist%20at%20heart%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20pass%20up%20the%20opportunity%20to%20see%20what%20all%20the%20fuss%20was%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20joined%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20learning%20a%20good%20bit.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20was%20on%20a%20team%20where%20software%20was%20the%20final%20product%20and%20not%20just%20an%20internal%20tool%20%E2%80%94%20where%20getting%20the%20last%20mile%20right%20really%20mattered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20a%20few%20months%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20wasn't%20learning%20anymore.%20There%20was%20a%20top-down%20management%20style%20and%20a%20nitpicky%2C%20boxed-in%20way%20of%20working.%20I%20worked%20on%20a%20lot%20of%20bugs%20and%20features%2C%20and%20when%20I%20asked%20to%20work%20on%20different%20projects%20that%20I%20wasn't%20familiar%20with%2C%20I%20was%20told%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20assume%20that%20if%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-market-nvidia-quarter-meeting-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ework%20at%20Nvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20My%20package%20was%20in%20the%20low%20six%20figures%2C%20and%20the%20wide%20disparities%20in%20pay%20between%20older%20and%20newer%20employees%20impacted%20the%20culture%20because%20we%20were%20all%20playing%20different%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20I%20view%20a%20job%20is%20I%20want%20to%20either%20be%20learning%20or%20earning.%20I%20joined%20late%20enough%20that%20the%20money%20wasn't%20life-changing%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20I%20could%20get%20another%20job%20that%20paid%20roughly%20the%20same%20amount%20if%20it%20ever%20came%20to%20that.%20Also%2C%20our%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20reasonable%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraleigh-durham-north-carolina-innovation-entrepreneurship-tech-workforce-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERaleigh-Durham%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20are%20both%20pretty%20fiscally%20shrewd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22540967df-7e89-4891-b0d1-225199add87c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EReconnecting%20with%20my%20love%20for%20technology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20knew%20I%20would%20launch%20my%20own%20company%20one%20day.%20One%20of%20my%20ambitions%20was%20to%20command%20my%20own%20time%20by%20the%20age%20of%2030%20and%20to%20have%20kids%20who%20could%20grow%20up%20seeing%20me%20do%20that%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20invested%20about%20%2420%2C000%20to%20found%20our%20family-owned%20cloud%20provider%2C%20Carolina%20Cloud.%20We're%20bootstrapping%20for%20now%2C%20but%20aren't%20opposed%20to%20raising%20a%20small%20round%20down%20the%20line%20if%20we%20fill%20our%20current%20server%20fleet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarolina%20Cloud%20does%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-microsoft-ai-gpu-blackwell-cooling-wasteful-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoffer%20GPUs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20we're%20focused%20on%20CPUs%20because%20we%20believe%20they%20absolutely%20aren't%20going%20anywhere%3A%20they're%20less%20finicky%2C%20use%20less%20power%2C%20are%20cheaper%2C%20and%20last%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20previous%20jobs%20where%20we'd%20rented%20cloud%2C%20the%20prices%20were%20so%20high%20compared%20to%20what%20I%20knew%20it%20would%20cost%20to%20actually%20build%20one%20of%20the%20computers%2C%20so%20I%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20create%20a%20provider%20that%20delivered%20value%20while%20still%20making%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarolina%20Cloud%20is%20focused%20on%20on-demand%2C%20high-performance%20compute.%20Some%20of%20our%20early%20customers%20are%20hedge%20funds%20and%20genomics%20companies%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-innovation-offices-raleigh-durham-north-carolina-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EResearch%20Triangle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20differentiate%20from%20hyperscalers%20with%20lower%20pricing%2C%20no%20egress%20fees%2C%20and%20high-touch%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuitting%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-ceo-criticism-nvidia-dgx-spark-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejob%20at%20Nvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20my%20mental%20health.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%2C%20I%20started%20sleeping%20better%2C%20chatting%20with%20strangers%20in%20public%2C%20spontaneously%20running%20errands%20I'd%20forgotten%20about%2C%20and%20calling%20people%20I%20hadn't%20thought%20about%20in%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20been%20working%20really%20hard%2C%20but%20on%20my%20own%20terms%2C%20which%20has%20allowed%20me%20to%20reconnect%20with%20my%20love%20for%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20takes%20time%20to%20get%20a%20business%20off%20the%20ground%2C%20I%20told%20myself%20that%20if%20we%20didn't%20turn%20a%20profit%20in%2018%20months%2C%20I%20could%20go%20back%20to%20a%20traditional%20job.%20But%20right%20now%2C%20early%20interest%20has%20gone%20as%20expected%20and%20indicates%20that%20we%20should%20be%20able%20to%20stay%20the%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Agweiss%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Egweiss%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20%40geoffweiss.25.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecure-news-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fadclick.g.doubleclick.net%2Fpcs%2Fclick%3Fxai%3DAKAOjsvWKWkiTMfHjtig0lFc1D1rUk00OQSO6QCntMHjZG6bBlcF_5XrHZ4gqdH84LLEosAUlGm23mQuyAOf75MhAz5hEV6eDqprpKU4MmmtmRRc4yCX9W1PKu8u_L4CkQn3Po7Lh8V00lLbIzAorTH9cGMLj4O5Ol852oTOAlW3iIbykdMe_cAsBufie_c6hmDOtgQ6tNWmUS99VozgBLTv97-t5tz0MmYXkiOIdS4r72jwIGOdPuYKUX1iyCg96_XzP_llavB6trHjSRVLQT6-2gLu5gqtIwZ6L__8F7wE1Vz-ktJNvgLpr4hDWjaYyuaOizB_R8VlSgnyIqYsEFuSN7wQ7f