C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Robotics%20showcase%20at%20WEF%20Davos%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6971ef3ad3c7faef0eccb713%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225174%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E5%20AI%20and%20trade%20experts%20at%20Davos%20share%20their%20thoughts%20on%20the%20future%20of%20Robotics.%3Cp%3EINA%20FASSBENDER%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDigital%20twins%20are%20delivering%20real%20productivity%20gains%20for%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELabor%20shortages%20are%20accelerating%20the%20need%20for%20humanoid%20robots.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETailored%20research%20and%20development%20is%20crucial%20for%20effective%20AI%20integration.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20of%20AI%20chatbots%20and%20agents%2C%20we're%20not%20talking%20enough%20about%20physical%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20Thursday%20morning%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavos-wef-live-updates-jan-22-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDavos%20panel%3C%2Fa%3E%20moderated%20by%20Business%20Insider's%20Jamie%20Heller%2C%20robotics%20experts%20dived%20into%20ways%20bots%20are%20going%20to%20change%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20and%20their%20key%20limitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20three%20takeaways%20from%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20panel%2C%20which%20featured%20robotics%20and%20automation%20experts%20and%20a%20trade%20minister%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245ed1b9a-f5f3-490f-948f-53b2ef5b6961%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Digital%20twins%20have%20moved%20from%20hype%20to%20real%20return%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20phrase%20dominated%20the%20conversation%3A%20digital%20twins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExecutives%20from%20Siemens%2C%20Agility%20Robotics%2C%20and%20Automation%20Anywhere%20agreed%20that%20what%20once%20sounded%20like%20a%20distant%20possibility%20is%20now%20delivering%20real%20productivity%20gains%20for%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20digital%20twin%20is%20a%20digital%20replica%20of%20a%20physical%20object%2C%20person%2C%20or%20process.%20They%20can%20help%20organizations%20simulate%20real%20situations%20and%20their%20outcomes%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20make%20better%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDigital%20twins%20have%20been%20around%2C%20but%20the%20technology%20has%20exponentially%20improved%2C%20and%20the%20computing%20power%20has%20exponentially%20improved%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Automation%20Anywhere%20CEO%20Mihir%20Shukla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BLet's%20say%20digital%20twins%20tell%20you%20that%20there%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20problem%20in%20manufacturing.%20You%20can%20proactively%20act%20on%20it.%20It%20has%20implications%20on%20your%20inventory.%20It%20has%20implications%20on%20your%20shipping%20planning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiemens'%20CEO%20Roland%20Busch%20said%20that%20the%20productivity%20boost%20is%20showing%20up%20in%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20company's%20output%20is%2020%25%20higher%20and%20that%20energy%20costs%20are%2020%25%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20much%2C%20much%20faster%20and%20ramping%20up%2C%20you%20don't%20make%20mistakes%2C%26quot%3B%20if%20you%20use%20a%20digital%20twin%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bcb4ef24-98be-473e-883c-f8fd026f7bb2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Labor%20shortages%20are%20driving%20humanoid%20robots%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhumanoid-robot-companies-us-tesla-figure-1x-agility-apptronik-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERobots%20can%3C%2Fa%3E%20do%20work%20that%20humans%20are%20unable%20to%20%E2%80%94%20or%20don't%20want%20to%20%E2%80%94%20do%2C%20said%20Peggy%20Johnson%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Agility%20Robotics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20hard%20to%20hire%20for%20these%20manual%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20dull%20and%20dirty%2C%20and%20they're%20dangerous%20at%20times%20because%20you're%20lifting%20over%20and%20over%20again%2C%20very%20repetitive.%20It's%20kind%20of%20mind-numbing%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFaster%20progress%20in%20robotics%20means%20a%20better%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20the%20humans%20who%20are%20doing%20such%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20injuries%20are%20also%20another%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20about%20jobs%20that%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20heavy%20lifting.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20an%20aging%20workforce.%20A%20lot%20of%20young%20kids%20don't%20want%20to%20go%20into%20environments%20like%20this.%20So%20the%20older%20employees%20are%20also%20getting%20hurt%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThani%20Ahmed%20Al%20Zeyoudi%2C%20the%20Minister%20of%20Foreign%20Trade%20for%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20echoed%20that%20robotics%20was%20the%20future%20of%20%26quot%3Bnon-skilled%26quot%3B%20labor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20too%20difficult%20to%20attract%20new%20young%20people%20to%20start%20working%20on%20the%20construction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BRobotics%20is%20the%20main%20solution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20building%20robots%20that%20are%20safe%20to%20use%20in%20human%20environments%20is%20also%20key%2C%20Johnson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e16cf22b-f753-44d2-8f43-245b3afb88d1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20You%20can't%20copy%20and%20paste%20R%26amp%3BD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAl%20Zeyoudi%20added%20that%20financing%20AI%20is%20only%20the%20first%20step%20toward%20AI%20integration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20you%20have%20the%20money%2C%20but%20you%20haven't%20diagnosed%20the%20right%20solution%20to%20the%20problem%20that%20you're%20having%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20UAE's%20push%20for%20AI%20includes%20government%20appointments%2C%20policy%20development%2C%20and%20research%20and%20development%2C%20which%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bmain%20game%20changer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%2C%20many%20stakeholders%20are%20avoiding%20that%20because%20they%20say%20someone%20else%20will%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20R%26amp%3BD.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20just%20copy%20and%20paste%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI%2C%20it's%20too%20late%2C%26quot%3B%20Al%20Zeyoudi%20added.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20start%20working%20on%20R%26amp%3BD%20because%20you%20ensure%20to%20customize%20things%20to%20your%20own%20ecosystem%2C%20your%20own%20environments%2C%20your%20own%20conditions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavos-panel-future-robotics-wef-automation-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1769075358000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6971ef5ea645d1188187c77c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavos-panel-future-robotics-wef-automation-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20panel%20moderated%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20robotics%20experts%20dove%20into%20how%20bots%20are%20going%20to%20change%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavos-panel-future-robotics-wef-automation-2026-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ganesh%20Jayanti%3A%20Iconic%20Bollywood%20Ganesh%20Songs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1769075241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-127136874%2Cimgsize-60522.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fganesh-jayanti-deva-ho-deva-jalwa-iconic-bollywood-ganesha-songs-that-bring-festivals-to-life%2Fphotostory%2F127136874.cms%22%2C%22s